Hypertext Module This is the XML Schema Hypertext module for XHTML * a This module declares the anchor ('a') element type, which defines the source of a hypertext link. The destination (or link 'target') is identified via its 'id' attribute rather than the 'name' attribute as was used in HTML. $Id$

<xs:documentation>
Hypertext Module
This is the XML Schema Hypertext module for XHTML

* a

This module declares the anchor ('a') element type, which
defines the source of a hypertext link. The destination
(or link 'target') is identified via its 'id' attribute
rather than the 'name' attribute as was used in HTML.

$Id$
